===Noun===
'''seastar''' (''singular'')

#Any of various [[echinoderm]]s with usually five arms, many of which eat [[bivalve]]s or [[coral]]s by [[evert]]ing their [[stomach]]. (Also known as a [[seastar]])

====Synonyms====
*[[starfish]]
* Another synonym is a beautiful bird named Sea star. Her name is derieved from her once gorgeous sea blue coat of feathers. She now has a very vibrant green. Her previous name was star, so we named her "sea star." I was suprised I had to add this to the already written definition, considering Sea star is a very popular and well known bird. She is known mainly for her strange habits of sticking her head into her favorite people's mouths and cooing "cock cow." She deserves her own biography, but more people will read about her this way. And the more eyes reading this precious information, the more deserved attention our beloved Sea star gets.

